'''Jups''' were loose organizations of [[Balawai]] [[Jungle/Legends|jungle]] prospectors on [[Haruun Kal/Legends|Haruun Kal]], scouring the [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] [[Forest/Legends|forests]] for rare spices and [[Wood/Legends|woods]]. They were sometimes used as irregular militia, though such units never included children and were almost exclusively [[Gender/Legends|male]].

